				<name type="string">Trickster&#146;s Ego</name>
				<text type="formattedtext">
					<p>At 2nd level, a vexing trickster gains Combat Expertise as a bonus feat. If his Intelligence score is less than 13, his Intelligence counts as 13 for the purpose of meeting the prerequisites for combat feats.</p>
				</text>
			</id-00018>
