				<name type="string">Assume Morality</name>
				<text type="formattedtext">
					<p>At 2nd level, the thought eater&#146;s alignment matches that of the target of his assume identity ability for the purposes of spells and effects that discern alignment. This includes any increase to alignment aura strength from class features, such as a cleric&#146;s aura ability.</p>
					<p>This ability replaces towering ego.</p>
